nodes.text: Hi,    My insurance will not allow me to opt out of using Org2 pharmacy for the anastrozle. I setup for them to ship the medication to me, however, I will not be receiving that refill between 5-10 business days. I am going to run out of the pills on MM/DD/YYYY, may I get like a 7 or 10 day supply called into Org2 in Org2? Thank you, Person1
